{"tid":828644,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[暴力足球合法化] C.朗姐姐伸冤！怒斥球證：有人要摧毀我細佬","createTime":"2018-09-19T23:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T01:30:20.000Z","uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2e18715e88425efda9e54741686a1d1a5e7b2d1d","tid":828644,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T23:57:43.000Z","msg":"在歐冠盃祖雲達斯2-0戰勝華倫西亞的比賽中，上半場第28分鐘，由於與梅里路發生衝突，C.朗拿度被球證紅牌罰下。<br />\n<br />\n賽後，這個判罰引起了極大的爭議，C.朗拿度的姐姐也出面討說法。比賽一結束，C.朗拿度姐姐katiaaveiro立即在Instagram上表達了不滿：這是足球的恥辱，（有人）想摧毀我細佬，但上帝不會打瞌睡的，真是恥辱。<br />\n<br />\n　　祖記未來的兩場比賽分別是在香港時間10月3日對陣年青人，以及在10月24日對陣曼聯。C.朗拿度將缺陣祖記下一場對年青人的比賽，但若歐洲足協追加懲罰，C.朗拿度將有可能錯過回曼聯主場的比賽。"},{"pid":"f2aa8b340347d64bbdcfb9c7967a96e21f1ac9bc","tid":828644,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T23:58:14.000Z","msg":"好勤力wor"},{"pid":"dbd4114aacf9856caa8e8182b635995894ce0062","tid":828644,"uid":147097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:04:03.000Z","msg":"入唔波就打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小左兩球擦數據12碼既雞會<br />\n<br />\nbtw無左佢又係輕取3分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a448e28ce20d96c5481a3ffeec433965812e785","tid":828644,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:04:42.000Z","msg":"王 sir 早晨"},{"pid":"8f5eb2ef5aafed5abfcc1175aa0f52c41b9b76ef","tid":828644,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:04:50.000Z","msg":"C朗 幾時多左個姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd65282933039aec3599dbb8d44bd70edd149b8","tid":828644,"uid":10176,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:05:43.000Z","msg":"王生變左西班牙鬥牛咁<br />\n一見到張紅牌興奮到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b722740e8df4f37dd15e7fcd00b6755c61cf08","tid":828644,"uid":34858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"